@NODE "Dist" "Distribution"
@TOC "MAIN"
Distribution
~~~~~~~~~~~~

    SPC (Screen Palette Control) is ©1995 André Osterhues.

    SPC is CardWare. So if you like SPC, please send me
    a postcard.

    The archive you just unpacked may be freely distributed,
    but you may not charge any money for it, except
    distribution costs (diskettes, postage etc.).

    The author can not be blamed for any damage caused by
